data.description: Full Bedroom & Bathroom on Main Level !!  3 Bedrooms (Primary plus 2 others) on Upper Level PLUS a Bonus Room w/ storage too.  Main Level boasts a full bedroom plus a full bathroom for visitors, a "Kitchen / Family" room combo with an eating area and eating bar at the granite kitchen counter and a pantry as well.  There is a living room and dining room off of the Entry, plus a laundry space between the entry and garage. Nice Lot with generously sized back yard, a brand new roof in April 2023 with a transferable warranty.  AND.. Potentially ASSUMABLE VA Mortgage at 2.875% - 27 years remaining. NOTE: Any qualified Buyer can assume an existing VA mortgage and does NOT need to be a veteran to do so.  Also, an assumption would save a Buyer thousands in loan costs (no origination fee, no appraisal).  Disclosure: Listing Realtor is related to Seller.
